WEBVTT

00:02.400 --> 00:04.756
Doctor, my baby girl
Hazel is sick.

00:04.760 --> 00:08.151
He said Kennedy shall be hung
by the neck until he be dead.

00:08.160 --> 00:10.436
Do you think your choices
will not haunt you?

00:10.440 --> 00:12.318
If you think
you'll intimidate me

00:12.320 --> 00:13.674
into dropping my bid,

00:13.680 --> 00:15.751
well, you're as stupid
as you are duplicitous!

00:15.760 --> 00:18.559
Lansing's out of control.
He must be contained.

00:18.560 --> 00:20.597
Is this official
police business, sir, or--

00:20.600 --> 00:23.593
What this is, Mr. Maguire,
is you showing appreciation

00:23.600 --> 00:25.114
for being saved
from the gallows!

00:25.120 --> 00:27.271
<i>- Missus Corcoran.
- I'm looking for Kevin.</i>

00:27.280 --> 00:30.273
Ellen stopped by today.
She's pregnant.

00:31.280 --> 00:33.636
You slept with my wife
again, you son of a bitch!

00:33.640 --> 00:35.279
The child is not mine,
Kevin.

00:37.000 --> 00:43.074
